# bugs (chronological discovery)

## BUG#1 — string ordering void return
@symptom topic="topic" on remote (e.g., 2026-04-27_topic_omega_cycle.json)
@root_cause Linux hexa_real returns void from str>=,<=,<,> (Mac stage0 returns bool)
@fix_call_site nexus/tool/kick_dispatch.hexa::_slugify (index_of replace)
@fix_binary_deep hexa-lang/tool/build_interp_linux.hexa cross-build
@binary_pre_sha256 65f87a79
@binary_post_sha256 2ce1ff03bfd8174c062e88918e0b2a78db3475f6ea4a596c2ac8500ba455adae
@bonus && short-circuit on empty array (also fixed by binary rebuild)

## BUG#2 — cross-runtime args() shape
@symptom mkfifo /tmp/subagent-relay-/path/-.fifo (parent_sid=script_path, child_sid=empty)
@root_cause args() shape — Mac stage0 [bin,bin,...] vs Linux hexa_real [bin,run,script.hexa,...]
@fix_call_site hive/tool/subagent_dispatch.hexa cross-runtime _ai skip
@fix_class hexa-lang/self/stdlib/argv_skip.hexa shared helper
@class_migrations 24 + 21 = 45 hive tools (sub-A + sub-E)
@latent_bug_revealed sub-A's helper deploy was incomplete on Linux (cwd-relative resolution); sub-E fixed via multi-path stdlib deploy

## BUG#3 — ai_err_exit undefined on Linux
@symptom Runtime error: undefined function: ai_err_exit on remote
@root_cause Mac sets HEXA_LANG globally; remote ssh shells inherit minimal env; ubu1 hexa-lang missing self/stdlib entirely
@fix_call_site nexus/scripts/bin/hexa_remote (HEXA_LANG inject in REMOTE_CMD)
@fix_data hexa-lang/self/stdlib/ rsync 19 files to ubu1+ubu2
@latent_finding sub-E discovered: Linux runtime ignores HEXA_LANG, uses cwd/script-dir resolution → multi-path stdlib deploy required

## BUG#4 — disown bash-only
@symptom sh: 1: disown: not found on remote (POSIX sh / dash)
@root_cause `disown` is bash builtin; nohup ... & alone sufficient for SIGHUP-immunity + background
@fix hive/tool/subagent_dispatch.hexa (removed both disown invocations)

## BUG#5 — credential propagation gap (surfaced by sub-C e2e)
@symptom hive coding-agent on ubu2 — "No API key found" — kick exits spawn-failed-rc-3
@root_cause ssh shell inherits minimal env; ANTHROPIC_API_KEY not propagated
@fix nexus/scripts/bin/hexa_remote — env passthrough $(printf %q "${ANTHROPIC_API_KEY:-}") + raw 66 pre-flight warning when unset
@user_action export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-... in ~/.zshrc

## BUG#6 — kick_bench flag propagation gap
@symptom bench used kick_dispatch defaults — raw 48 K≥3 axes orthogonality not exercised
@fix nexus/tool/kick_bench.hexa — added --axes/--noise/--stratum forward (3 flag parsers + 3 forward lines)

## BUG#7 (binary deep) — Linux hexa_real stale
@symptom binary on ubu1/ubu2 was pre-fix (1598952 bytes, BuildID 0cb34e4d…)
@root_cause Source fix da5ee622 (2026-04-24) committed but binary never rebuilt
@fix sub-D cross-built via tool/build_interp_linux.hexa (musl-static, 2093728 bytes), redeployed ubu1/ubu2 with chattr +i, backups at ~/.hx/bin/hexa_real.pre-r4-bug1-fix.bak

